fields.Description/Abstract:
Conducted 24, auditioned college flute players at the National Flute Association Convention.  Chose program, and lead 8 hours of rehearsals.

All videos of this concert can be found at Nicole Molumby Youtube Channel.

I led the creation of three newly commissioned works through two different consortium.  These works were premiered at the NFA Convention:

Ancient Impressions for flute choir by Blaz Pucihar

Between Angles for flute choir by Cynthia Folio

Air and Funk for flute choir by Bob Washut
